{"tid":2135794,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"請問有冇It大神可以救下我？","createTime":"2020-08-01T16:54:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-03T00:02:54.000Z","uid":268206,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"aac148320974374e65f3d7ccf21af48c64a38848","tid":2135794,"uid":268206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T16:54:54.000Z","msg":"各位巴絲打，我部desktop 經常性出現三個問題：<br />\n<br />\n1，突然出現藍屏<br />\n2，開機boot 唔起機（係開機windows 畫面不停打⭕️，然後係電腦運行狀態嘅黑屏）<br />\n3，開機成功開到，但一開software 就會lag 死<br />\n<br />\n請問呢個情況下，咩硬件壞嘅可能性最大？<br />\nDisplay (新買，1660 super)<br />\nRam (8G x 2)<br />\nCPU(i5-7500)<br />\nHD(500G)<br />\n底板（平價底板，Msi-H110)<br />\n我係正常開機情況下check 過，display,兩條ram都冇問題，但cpu 好似異常高（冇software 開緊下使用率29%）<br />\n板板or CPU 壞嘅可能性大？"},{"pid":"053d6871e34941c7b2212b7676b9357bde7bcd08","tid":2135794,"uid":268206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T17:00:56.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31b9d05b7ecbbd9a610748df485551f51f32c0cf","tid":2135794,"uid":146476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T17:37:37.000Z","msg":"可能喺板/HDD.   <br />\n解決方法，換曬佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"543cdcb57498533a4d3c5100109b6486082acf7f","tid":2135794,"uid":5299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T17:38:32.000Z","msg":"hdd"},{"pid":"f08e80f644745045c77ee0b8fbe9465ba9e5343d","tid":2135794,"uid":118709,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T17:52:25.000Z","msg":"IT人=電腦水電維修員 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1c33b96cdc53075f0cdf004bb99156f405a2e3d","tid":2135794,"uid":268206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31b9d05b7ecbbd9a610748df485551f51f32c0cf","tid":2135794,"uid":146476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T17:37:37.000Z","msg":"可能喺板/HDD.   <br />\n解決方法，換曬佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor